{"tid":2064884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿旦facebook 新相真係好撚正","createTime":"2020-06-15T06:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:59:09.000Z","uid":4646,"like":57,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"03dbcf59bf8796e86efe65905a9ae0408c8ff0b4","tid":2064884,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/104098804_3005054356207455_7713733865897558484_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkbtlJIJOyVqkV_x42agxK99Tz526L7CntcuwKmzR3vT9WVXM5siZI8xO1uqT3pBVE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=f12f8fc1f53f9a6204ecdd01ed0fc7f6&amp;oe=5F0AD6CB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F104098804_3005054356207455_7713733865897558484_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkbtlJIJOyVqkV_x42agxK99Tz526L7CntcuwKmzR3vT9WVXM5siZI8xO1uqT3pBVE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D14%26oh%3Df12f8fc1f53f9a6204ecdd01ed0fc7f6%26oe%3D5F0AD6CB&h=3d78f5c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78193a3a9119f84bea52d82f6a66925923d2d21d","tid":2064884,"uid":4646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:32:56.000Z","msg":"愛愛聲吵到鄰居，確實是有缺公德啦﹗但這也證明這位女生的魅力和誘惑度，畢竟要跟同一個人夜夜笙歌，可是要有足夠的魅力，才可以讓男伴保持精力一直勇往直前。擁有32E驕人上圍的香港女生鄧伊玲（Elaine），就可以這樣跟鄰居「分享」她的「喜悅」。<br />\n<br />\n離開了男友的阿旦，表示自己不會怪責男友。後來聽說前男友有意結婚，也公開祝福對方，還表示自己也已經開啓了另一頁，跟其他人有新發展。阿旦之後搬出與前男友的合居之地時，也被媒體拍到有壯男幫她搬東西，之前還多次留宿過夜。據稱有一段時間，該社區多次傳出女性瘋狂愛愛的聲音，對鄰居造成困擾，成為大家的討論話題。但阿旦否認該叫床的女性是自己，但這樣火辣的女生，身邊有男伴也很正常吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbac4c6f0d7f9864ae06be3b8184c6a5ef53e21","tid":2064884,"uid":4646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/12-12-2019/t_bd53b434d3a74f6e93be971e09aaec8b_name_15